headline: RBC and DoorDash extend program to deliver new and greater value for more Canadians
summary: Royal Bank of Canada (RBC) and DoorDash are extending their long-standing program to provide complimentary access to DashPass, DoorDash's subscription service, offering even more value to eligible** RBC credit cardholders as well as Avion Rewards members. Through DashPass, customers receive $0 delivery fees and reduced service fees on eligible* delivery orders via DoorDash, plus other perks like exclusive savings opportunities.
